WEBVTT

00:02.956 --> 00:05.795
As soon as she goes into labour,
you're induced.

00:05.796 --> 00:07.875
Discretion bought, and you emerge

00:07.876 --> 00:10.875
with a bonny bouncing babe
in your arms.

00:10.876 --> 00:13.555
Don't make me ask, please.

00:13.556 --> 00:16.196
Jack? He is your father.

00:18.356 --> 00:20.115
And this new man is, what,

00:20.116 --> 00:22.195
some misguided attempt
to make George jealous?

00:22.196 --> 00:25.556
I'll be appealing to a far more
potent emotion than that.

00:26.716 --> 00:28.395
Regina's back.

00:28.396 --> 00:30.435
They say your husband's alive.

00:30.436 --> 00:32.195
You bring him home.

00:32.195 --> 00:34.196
I love you.

00:35.196 --> 00:36.716
I always will.

00:44.054 --> 00:45.925
I'm here Rene.

